### Test Email Generation API

# 1. Generate Single Email Draft
POST http://localhost:3000/emails/generation/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactId": 1,
  "summaryId": 1,
  "clientEmailId": 1,
  "tone": "pro_friendly"
}

###

# 2. Generate Professional Tone Email
POST http://localhost:3000/emails/generation/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactId": 2,
  "summaryId": 2,
  "clientEmailId": 1,
  "tone": "professional"
}

###

# 3. Generate Friendly Tone Email
POST http://localhost:3000/emails/generation/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactId": 1,
  "summaryId": 1,
  "clientEmailId": 1,
  "tone": "friendly"
}

###

# 4. Get Generated Email Draft
GET http://localhost:3000/emails/generation/drafts/1

###

# 5. Create Email Campaign
POST http://localhost:3000/emails/campaign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Campaign - Tech Companies",
  "description": "Outreach to technology companies for cloud solutions",
  "contactIds": [1, 2],
  "clientEmailId": 1,
  "tone": "pro_friendly"
}

###

# 6. Get Email Templates
GET http://localhost:3000/emails/templates

###

# 7. Get Campaign Details
GET http://localhost:3000/emails/campaigns/campaign_1738000000000

###

# 8. Get Email Analytics
GET http://localhost:3000/emails/analytics?contactId=1

